{"tid":2101331,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"傳今年內在港上市 千億美元估值螞蟻集團再否認IPO傳聞","createTime":"2020-07-09T16:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T16:55:44.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f36e77189a59f571471f950564eeca723d8fd5e","tid":2101331,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2690000/2690012/a4477e30-3219-4a8b-a7eb-f13af944af57_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2690000%2F2690012%2Fa4477e30-3219-4a8b-a7eb-f13af944af57_1024_1024.jpg&h=ff7fa80b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地傳媒引述消息指，支付寶母公司、阿里系的螞蟻科技集團（前稱螞蟻金服）計劃最早於今年在香港上市，目標估值為2000億美元。報道稱，螞蟻集團非常傾向先在香港上市。惟螞蟻集團表示，有關IPO傳聞「消息不實」；阿里巴巴 則對此不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n今年以來，市場屢次傳出螞蟻集團計劃上市。年初有英國媒體引述消息指，螞蟻集團與瑞信、中金正在籌備上市事項，並指螞蟻集團計劃在A股及H股同步上市。報道又稱，螞蟻集團原計劃2018年上市，但受制監管不明朗、盈利能力等憂慮而擱置。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，據當時的報道，螞蟻集團去年進行股權融資140億美元，當時估值達1500億美元，而這次內地傳媒引述的目標估值為2000億美元，增加了33.3%。<br />\n<br />\n螞蟻集團是全球價值最高科技「獨角獸」，2018年螞蟻集團最後一輪籌資給予該公司約1500億美元估值，去年底次級市場小型交易給予螞蟻集團的隱含估值則達到2000億美元。<span class=\"red\">路透取得的財務文件顯示，螞蟻集團去年營收約1200億元人民幣，純益逼近170億元人民幣</span>。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2690012/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2690012%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=294cf631\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2690012/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20200708/OPQEQEDCMTQ47MRQZUWB555FC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20200708%2FOPQEQEDCMTQ47MRQZUWB555FC4%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=1dee9975\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20200708%2FOPQEQEDCMTQ47MRQZUWB555FC4%2F&h=7a7802ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20200708/OPQEQEDCMTQ47MRQZUWB555FC4/</a>"},{"pid":"d2e31d81b47ba0a56c94ba22d2cf42c65f2c8f99","tid":2101331,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:43:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ce630285f443071511bfecee16a106181cd0779","tid":2101331,"uid":137569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d2e31d81b47ba0a56c94ba22d2cf42c65f2c8f99","tid":2101331,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:43:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:55:44.000Z","msg":"其實呢個宣傳好唔得<br />\n可唔可以有啲美感同設計"}]}